summary: The document is a CIA Information Telegram from July 12, 1963, included in the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Collection Act of 1992. It forms part of the National Security Files with a specific focus on Vietnam during 1963. The document was last reviewed on September 10, 2000, indicating its scrutiny under the Assassination Records Act.
key_findings: Document is part of the JFK Assassination Records Collection.
Originates from the CIA and is dated July 12, 1963.
Pertains to National Security Files with a focus on Vietnam.
Last reviewed on September 10, 2000, indicating it has been subject to scrutiny under the Assassination Records Act.
